Rule 13    statement -> OPCODE register COMMA register COMMA LABEL NEWLINE
Rule 14    register -> REGISTER
Rule 15    statement -> NEWLINE

Terminals, with rules where they appear

COLUMN               : 2
COMMA                : 8 8 9 9 10 11 12 13 13
DIRECTIVE            : 5 6 7
IMMEDIATE            : 6 9 10 11
LABEL                : 2 5 12 13
LPAREN               : 10
NEWLINE              : 2 3 5 6 7 8 9 10 11 12 13 15
OPCODE               : 8 9 10 11 12 13
REGISTER             : 14
